name: From The Sidewalk Of New York
description:
These photos are taken back in 2019, while I visit my parents who lives in New York City. It is probably the last time I’ve seen the city or my parents and sister, until I renew my visa for United States of America.

All photos are taken with Yashica 109MP with only one roll of film; the Kodak Vision 3 500T.

I hope you can enjoy the photos that I taken and compose in this (so-called) zine.

21 Photos
16 Pages
------------

If you live in Indonesia and collected my works, I will send the print right to your front door.
